snippet.title: The Key of Avalon 1.0 Opening
snippet.description: Just uploaded for completion as its not on youtube as far as I can see, extracted from the triforce disc GDT-0006G. The one I previously uploaded was actually the opening for 1.2/1.3 and this is the "original" 1.0 opening.
